56static int input_kex_dh_gex_request(int, u_int32_t, struct ssh *);
57static int input_kex_dh_gex_init(int, u_int32_t, struct ssh *);
58
59int
60kexgex_server(struct ssh *ssh)
61{
62 ssh_dispatch_set(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_REQUEST,
63 &input_kex_dh_gex_request);
64 debug("expecting SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_REQUEST");
65 return 0;
66}
67
68static int
69input_kex_dh_gex_request(int type, u_int32_t seq, struct ssh *ssh)
70{
71 struct kex *kex = ssh->kex;
72 int r;
73 u_int min = 0, max = 0, nbits = 0;
74 const BIGNUM *dh_p, *dh_g;
75
76 debug("SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_REQUEST received");
77 if ((r = sshpkt_get_u32(ssh, &min)) != 0 ||
78 (r = sshpkt_get_u32(ssh, &nbits)) != 0 ||
79 (r = sshpkt_get_u32(ssh, &max)) != 0 ||
80 (r = sshpkt_get_end(ssh)) != 0)
81 goto out;
82 kex->nbits = nbits;
83 kex->min = min;
84 kex->max = max;
85 min = MAXIMUM(DH_GRP_MIN, min);
86 max = MINIMUM(DH_GRP_MAX, max);
87 nbits = MAXIMUM(DH_GRP_MIN, nbits);
88 nbits = MINIMUM(DH_GRP_MAX, nbits);
89
90 if (kex->max < kex->min || kex->nbits < kex->min ||
91 kex->max < kex->nbits || kex->max < DH_GRP_MIN) {
92 r = SSH_ERR_DH_GEX_OUT_OF_RANGE;
93 goto out;
94 }
95
96 /* Contact privileged parent */
97 kex->dh = PRIVSEP(choose_dh(min, nbits, max));
98 if (kex->dh == NULL) {
99 sshpkt_disconnect(ssh, "no matching DH grp found");
100 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
101 goto out;
102 }
103 debug("SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_GROUP sent");
104 DH_get0_pqg(kex->dh, &dh_p, NULL, &dh_g);
105 if ((r = sshpkt_start(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_GROUP)) != 0 ||
106 (r = sshpkt_put_bignum2(ssh, dh_p)) != 0 ||
107 (r = sshpkt_put_bignum2(ssh, dh_g)) != 0 ||
108 (r = sshpkt_send(ssh)) != 0)
109 goto out;
110
111 /* Compute our exchange value in parallel with the client */
112 if ((r = dh_gen_key(kex->dh, kex->we_need * 8)) != 0)
113 goto out;
114
115 debug("expecting SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_INIT");
116 ssh_dispatch_set(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_INIT, &input_kex_dh_gex_init);
117 r = 0;
118 out:
119 return r;
120}
121
122static int
123input_kex_dh_gex_init(int type, u_int32_t seq, struct ssh *ssh)
124{
125 struct kex *kex = ssh->kex;
126 BIGNUM *dh_client_pub = NULL;
127 const BIGNUM *pub_key, *dh_p, *dh_g;
128 struct sshbuf *shared_secret = NULL;
129 struct sshbuf *server_host_key_blob = NULL;
130 struct sshkey *server_host_public, *server_host_private;
131 u_char *signature = NULL;
132 u_char hash[SSH_DIGEST_MAX_LENGTH];
133 size_t slen, hashlen;
134 int r;
135
136 if ((r = kex_load_hostkey(ssh, &server_host_private,
137 &server_host_public)) != 0)
138 goto out;
139
140 /* key, cert */
141 if ((r = sshpkt_get_bignum2(ssh, &dh_client_pub)) != 0 ||
142 (r = sshpkt_get_end(ssh)) != 0)
143 goto out;
144 if ((shared_secret = sshbuf_new()) == NULL) {
145 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
146 goto out;
147 }
148 if ((r = kex_dh_compute_key(kex, dh_client_pub, shared_secret)) != 0)
149 goto out;
150 if ((server_host_key_blob = sshbuf_new()) == NULL) {
151 r = SSH_ERR_ALLOC_FAIL;
152 goto out;
153 }
154 if ((r = sshkey_putb(server_host_public, server_host_key_blob)) != 0)
155 goto out;
156
157 /* calc H */
158 DH_get0_key(kex->dh, &pub_key, NULL);
159 DH_get0_pqg(kex->dh, &dh_p, NULL, &dh_g);
160 hashlen = sizeof(hash);
161 if ((r = kexgex_hash(
162 kex->hash_alg,
163 kex->client_version,
164 kex->server_version,
165 kex->peer,
166 kex->my,
167 server_host_key_blob,
168 kex->min, kex->nbits, kex->max,
169 dh_p, dh_g,
170 dh_client_pub,
171 pub_key,
172 sshbuf_ptr(shared_secret), sshbuf_len(shared_secret),
173 hash, &hashlen)) != 0)
174 goto out;
175
176 /* sign H */
177 if ((r = kex->sign(ssh, server_host_private, server_host_public,
178 &signature, &slen, hash, hashlen, kex->hostkey_alg)) < 0)
179 goto out;
180
181 /* send server hostkey, DH pubkey 'f' and signed H */
182 if ((r = sshpkt_start(ssh, SSH2_MSG_KEX_DH_GEX_REPLY)) != 0 ||
183 (r = sshpkt_put_stringb(ssh, server_host_key_blob)) != 0 ||
184 (r = sshpkt_put_bignum2(ssh, pub_key)) != 0 || /* f */
185 (r = sshpkt_put_string(ssh, signature, slen)) != 0 ||
186 (r = sshpkt_send(ssh)) != 0)
187 goto out;
188
189 if ((r = kex_derive_keys(ssh, hash, hashlen, shared_secret)) == 0)
190 r = kex_send_newkeys(ssh);
191 out:
192 explicit_bzero(hash, sizeof(hash));
193 DH_free(kex->dh);
194 kex->dh = NULL;
195 BN_clear_free(dh_client_pub);
196 sshbuf_free(shared_secret);
197 sshbuf_free(server_host_key_blob);
198 free(signature);
199 return r;
200}
